{"tid":1117779,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"飛虎隊自發撐學生 被屈流氓地痞","createTime":"2019-04-21T02:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T11:02:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be969a6c7a10da466711258c47cc1cc3ecfdb8d5","tid":1117779,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T02:54:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190421/20660814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F20660814&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAtT2hWdA4JmoO%2FtHFZtOkv0%3D&h=9592e03c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F20660814&h=881e11f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190421/20660814</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飛虎隊自發撐學生 被屈流氓地痞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190421/large/a703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190421%2Flarge%2Fa703a.gif&h=ec575c73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當晚不少人用單車運送傷者到附近醫院。<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】1989年民運期間，北京民眾自發組成的電單車隊，為學生運送物資、振士氣。自北京進入戒嚴狀態後，「飛虎隊」便四處傳遞軍隊進城的消息，呼籲民眾前往阻攔。不過「飛虎隊」之名看似威風，但當時遭官媒點名批評，斥責飛虎隊由「極少數人糾集流氓地痞」組織而成，聯同上千輛單車的「敢死隊」，「像法國大革命那樣，攻打巴士底獄」。六四過後，一些成員更遭到重判。<br />\n<br />\n王麗玲表示，初時民間並沒有所謂「成立」過甚麼隊伍，純粹是每天晚飯後，民眾騎電單車到天安門廣場兜風，漸漸形成習慣。很多人覺得不過癮，特別是北京市政府出動直升機撒傳單後，民眾自發以電單車流以示對抗，支持學生。據王所述，最多聚集時達180架左右；車隊另一主要人物宋書元曾指平均每天有200架。而且當時沒有帶頭人，「都是誰的車排氣量大誰威風，誰就走在前邊」。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台/新華社  <br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：撿戒嚴隊頭盔 少年交出遭收監<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n撿戒嚴隊頭盔 少年交出遭收監<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n學運領袖候審病重 當局拒醫<br />\n<br />\n撿戒嚴隊頭盔 少年交出遭收監<br />\n學運領袖候審病重 當局拒醫<br />\n獨立筆會成員訪港遭國保阻撓<br />\n救人女飛虎還原血腥真相「屠城夜屍臭遍胡同」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4ccf86779b54dc0657838ab94e43be20731431","tid":1117779,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"仆街, 以為香港飛虎隊"}]}